<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/02-15.jpg" alt="02-15.jpg" ></p></center>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/02-16.jpg" alt="02-16.jpg" ></p></center>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/02-17-01.jpg" alt="02-17-01.jpg" ></p></center>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/02-17-02.jpg" alt="02-17-02.jpg" ></p></center>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/02-17-03.jpg" alt="02-17-03.jpg" ></p></center>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/02-17-04.jpg" alt="02-17-04.jpg" ></p></center>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/02-18.jpg" alt="02-18.jpg" ></p></center>
<p>以及各种形状怪异的石头。。。</p>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/02-19.jpg" alt="02-19.jpg" ></p></center>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/02-20.jpg" alt="02-20.jpg" ></p></center>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/02-21.jpg" alt="02-21.jpg" ></p></center>
<p>最后，我们在这里看了落日与晚霞。</p>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/02-22.jpg" alt="02-22.jpg" ></p></center>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/02-23.jpg" alt="02-23.jpg" ></p></center>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/02-24.jpg" alt="02-24.jpg" ></p></center>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/02-25.jpg" alt="02-25.jpg" ></p></center>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/02-26.jpg" alt="02-26.jpg" ></p></center>
<p>晚上住进了一个可以泡脚的宾馆，他们都说太贴心了，但是我并没有泡。。</p>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/02-27.jpg" alt="02-27.jpg" ></p></center>
<h2 id="day-3---张掖至敦煌">Day 3 - 张掖至敦煌</h2>
<p>从张掖驱车去敦煌。路上，三个北京人纠结了很久要不要进去嘉峪关，毕竟北京的长城都去了好多遍了。最后还是决定去了，感觉不虚此行！</p>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/03-01.jpg" alt="03-01.jpg" ></p></center>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/03-02.jpg" alt="03-02.jpg" ></p></center>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/03-03.jpg" alt="03-03.jpg" ></p></center>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/03-04.jpg" alt="03-04.jpg" ></p></center>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/03-05.jpg" alt="03-05.jpg" ></p></center>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/03-06.jpg" alt="03-06.jpg" ></p></center>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/03-07.jpg" alt="03-07.jpg" ></p></center>
