<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/03-10.jpg" alt="03-10.jpg" ></p></center>
<p>路过瓜州，网红景点，大地之子，不能错过。</p>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/03-11.jpg" alt="03-11.jpg" ></p></center>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/03-12.jpg" alt="03-12.jpg" ></p></center>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/03-13.jpg" alt="03-13.jpg" ></p></center>
<p>还有一个尾行别人爬坡，并冲下山坡摔伤的男人。据说，影响了『弗兰克的香瓜子』视频号的更新。</p>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/03-14.jpg" alt="03-14.jpg" ></p></center>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/03-15.jpg" alt="03-15.jpg" ></p></center>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/03-16.jpg" alt="03-16.jpg" ></p></center>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/03-17.jpg" alt="03-17.jpg" ></p></center>
<p>晚上，去看『又见敦煌』，还是很不错的。后悔没有带相机进去，少拍了好多演(mei)员(nv)的照片。。</p>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/03-18.jpg" alt="03-18.jpg" ></p></center>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/03-19.jpg" alt="03-19.jpg" ></p></center>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/03-20.jpg" alt="03-20.jpg" ></p></center>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/03-21.jpg" alt="03-21.jpg" ></p></center>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/03-22.jpg" alt="03-22.jpg" ></p></center>
<p>晚上十点多了，去了瓜州夜市，街里面各种吆喝，选了一家，吃到了第二天。。</p>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/03-23.jpg" alt="03-23.jpg" ></p></center>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/03-24.jpg" alt="03-24.jpg" ></p></center>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/03-25.jpg" alt="03-25.jpg" ></p></center>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/03-26.jpg" alt="03-26.jpg" ></p></center>
<p>住在了市中心的飞天幼儿园的旁边，这里有反弹琵琶。</p>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/03-27.jpg" alt="03-27.jpg" ></p></center>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/03-28.jpg" alt="03-28.jpg" ></p></center>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/03-29.jpg" alt="03-29.jpg" ></p></center>
<h2 id="day-4---敦煌">Day 4 - 敦煌</h2>
<p>在敦煌吃了一顿非常丰盛的早餐，简直硬到了极致。</p>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/04-01.jpg" alt="04-01.jpg" ></p></center>
<p>驱车去莫高窟。莫高窟并没有特别拍，因为禁止拍照。去看了特窟，总体上特别喜欢壁画的花纹。</p>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/04-02.jpg" alt="04-02.jpg" ></p></center>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/04-03.jpg" alt="04-03.jpg" ></p></center>
