<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/04-06.jpg" alt="04-06.jpg" ></p></center>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/04-07.jpg" alt="04-07.jpg" ></p></center>
<center><p><img src="/posts/2023/qing-gan-grand-loop/04-08.jpg" alt="04-08.jpg" ></p></center>
